ENSafrica ProBono and ProBono.Org are hosting a 419 scams and other financial frauds session at Isivivana Centre. The event will take place on Wednesday 12 July 2016, at 08 Mzala Street, Khayelitsha, and the function will start at 11am. The speaker for this session is Msizi Mcanyana from ENSafrica. For queries please call 021 397 4241. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  